c: 65
v: 7
t: "lynfq alzawj mimaa wssae allah ealayh ealaa zawjatih almtlqt, waealaa waladih 'iidha kan alzawj dha saeat fi alrzq, wamin duyiq ealayh fi alrizq wahu alfqyr, falyunfiq mimaa aetah allah min alrzq, la yukallaf alfaqir mithl ma yukallaf alghny, sayajeal allah baed dayq wshdt saeat wghna"